sequenceDiagram
    actor User as 🌍 User (Browser)
    participant CF as 🌐 CloudFlare<br/>CDN + WAF
    participant ALB as ⚖️ AWS ALB
    participant Kong as 🔀 Kong Gateway
    participant Istio as 🕸️ Istio Sidecar
    participant Auth as 🔐 Auth Service
    participant FE as 🌐 Next.js Frontend
    participant Product as 📦 Product Service
    participant Cart as 🛒 Cart Service
    participant Order as 📋 Order Service
    participant Payment as 💳 Payment Service
    participant Inventory as 📊 Inventory Service
    participant Notify as 🔔 Notify Service
    participant Kafka as 📨 Kafka
    participant DB as 🗄️ Aurora PostgreSQL
    participant Redis as ⚡ Redis Cache
    participant Jaeger as 🔍 Jaeger Tracing

    Note over User,Jaeger: 🛒 Customer Purchase Flow — Distributed Trace ID: trace-abc-123

    User->>CF: GET /products?q=laptop (HTTPS)
    CF->>CF: WAF check, DDoS filter, Cache lookup
    CF->>ALB: Forward request (X-Forwarded-For)
    ALB->>Kong: Route to Kong (TLS terminated)
    Kong->>Kong: Rate limit check (1000 req/min)
    Kong->>Kong: JWT validation (Bearer token)
    Kong->>Istio: Forward with trace headers
    Istio->>Istio: mTLS handshake, inject trace span
    Istio->>Auth: Validate token (gRPC)
    Auth->>Redis: Check token cache
    Redis-->>Auth: Token valid (cache hit)
    Auth-->>Istio: 200 OK — user: john@example.com
    Istio->>FE: Authenticated request
    FE->>Product: GET /api/products?q=laptop
    Product->>Redis: Check product cache
    Redis-->>Product: Cache miss
    Product->>DB: SELECT * FROM products WHERE...
    DB-->>Product: 24 results
    Product->>Redis: Cache results (TTL: 300s)
    Product-->>FE: 200 OK — product list
    FE-->>User: Render product page (SSR)
    FE->>Jaeger: Export trace span

    Note over User,Jaeger: 🛒 Add to Cart

    User->>Kong: POST /cart/items {productId, qty}
    Kong->>Istio: Forward authenticated
    Istio->>Cart: POST /items
    Cart->>Redis: HSET cart:{userId} product:123 qty:1
    Redis-->>Cart: OK
    Cart-->>User: 200 OK — cart updated

    Note over User,Jaeger: 💳 Checkout & Payment

    User->>Kong: POST /orders/checkout
    Kong->>Istio: Forward
    Istio->>Order: POST /checkout
    Order->>Cart: GET /cart/{userId}
    Cart->>Redis: HGETALL cart:{userId}
    Redis-->>Cart: Cart items
    Cart-->>Order: Cart data
    Order->>Inventory: POST /reserve {items}
    Inventory->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION — reserve stock
    DB-->>Inventory: Stock reserved
    Inventory-->>Order: Reservation confirmed
    Order->>Payment: POST /charge {amount, card}
    Payment->>Payment: Tokenize card (Stripe/Braintree)
    Payment->>DB: INSERT payment_intents
    Payment-->>Order: Payment authorized
    Order->>DB: INSERT orders (status: confirmed)
    Order->>Kafka: Publish order.created event
    Kafka-->>Notify: Consume order.created
    Notify->>Notify: Send confirmation email
    Order-->>User: 201 Created — order #ORD-789
    Order->>Jaeger: Export full trace (12 spans)
